Version 2.14:
- [+] 12 Apr 2005, Sheriff - Improvement: When the quantity of a cart item was grew and the condition of a special offer didn't apply any more a customer got two product items in his cart which were the same product but had different quantities. Now when the condition of a special offer doesn't apply any more the cart items that belong to the same product are combined into one item whose quantity is a sum of the quantities of both the products with an applied special offer and the products with no special offers applied. 
